143
00:10:20,070 --> 00:10:20,690
Wrong?

144
00:10:20,690 --> 00:10:22,910
I’m never wrong about you.

145
00:10:23,040 --> 00:10:24,900
If I could choose,

146
00:10:24,900 --> 00:10:26,080
I would choose

147
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:27,600
not to know you at all.

148
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:30,670
Really?

149
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:32,080
Without me,

150
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:33,750
