Good. Very well.

164
00:11:35,910 --> 00:11:37,690
I’ve found a young lady

165
00:11:37,910 --> 00:11:39,220
who’s carrying

166
00:11:39,220 --> 00:11:40,350
the wood bead with her

167
00:11:40,350 --> 00:11:42,490
that you made

168
00:11:42,640 --> 00:11:45,210
and used to be worn by Luo He.

169
00:11:45,210 --> 00:11:46,330
How old is she?

170
00:11:46,330 --> 00:11:47,600
16 or 17 years old.

171
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:51,440
Did you check her out?

172
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:52,340
Yes.

173
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:55,650
But too bad,

174
00:11:56,190 --> 00:11:57,600
she has a memory loss.

175
00:11:58,200 --> 00:11:59,560
So she doesn’t remember

176
00:11:59,870 --> 00:12:01,730
what happened before.

177
00:12:02,220 --> 00:12:02,750
What a shame!

178
00:12:02,750 --> 00:12:03,920
Memory loss?

179
00:12:06,160 --> 00:12:07,260
How skilled is she?

180
00:12:07,260 --> 00:12:08,440
No inner power.

181
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:10,230
Her style of kung fu is different from yours.

182
00:12:12,350 --> 00:12:13,570
Did she

183
00:12:14,850 --> 00:12:16,470
hide that on purpose?

184
00:12:16,470 --> 00:12:18,240
Do you really think a young lady

185
00:12:18,750 --> 00:12:21,530
can hide that when she was between life and death?

186
00:12:23,750 --> 00:12:25,400
Where is she right now?

187
00:12:29,230 --> 00:12:30,740
Where is she?

188
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:32,830
Do you think

189
00:12:32,830 --> 00:12:34,120
I will tell you that now?

190
00:12:34,590 --> 00:12:36,190
Will she still be alive

191
00:12:36,390 --> 00:12:37,790
if I tell you?

192
00:12:43,050 --> 00:12:43,970
Rest assured.

193
00:12:44,780 --> 00:12:45,660
You have my word.

194
00:12:46,050 --> 00:12:47,070
I will get to the bottom

195
00:12:47,070 --> 00:12:48,310
for you.

196
00:12:48,570 --> 00:12:49,810
If she is really the little killer

197
00:12:49,810 --> 00:12:51,800
who assassinated Luo He,

198
00:12:52,760 --> 00:12:53,830
I will certainly

199
00:12:53,830 --> 00:12:54,640
give her to you.

200
00:12:56,030 --> 00:12:57,160
If she is not…

201
00:12:58,160 --> 00:12:59,870
If she is not,

202
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:01,520
what will you do?

203
00:13:06,350 --> 00:13:07,630
If she is not,

204
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:11,140
I will protect her with my life.

205
00:13:24,050 --> 00:13:25,150
Zhong Yu.

206
00:13:26,360 --> 00:13:27,350
What brings you here?

207
00:13:27,460 --> 00:13:29,230
Marquis sent me here

208
00:13:29,230 --> 00:13:30,290
to pick you up.

209
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:33,070
What happened?

210
00:13:46,820 --> 00:13:48,210
To my son Yan Xun.

211
00:13:48,210 --> 00:13:50,580
We’ve parted for years. I miss you so much.

212
00:13:50,780 --> 00:13:53,790
I’m old and sick and looking forward to your return.

213
00:13:54,160 --> 00:13:56,490
I am aware that you’re held as a hostage

214
00:13:56,490 --> 00:13:57,980
and if you leave Chang’an openly,

215
00:13:57,980 --> 00:13:59,640
it will definitely set Emperor off.

216
00:13:59,640 --> 00:14:01,290
So I’m sending Zhong Yu

217
00:14:01,290 --> 00:14:03,710
to help you come home secretly

218
00:14:03,710 --> 00:14:06,470
so that we can finally reunite.

219
00:14:08,660 --> 00:14:10,220
Father wants me to go back with you?

220
00:14:11,610 --> 00:14:12,720
I know it came all too sudden

221
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:13,380
but please try to understand

222
00:14:13,380 --> 00:14:14,620
your father’s yearning

223
00:14:14,620 --> 00:14:15,950
and work with me.

224
00:14:19,650 --> 00:14:21,030
What’s he thinking?

225
00:14:21,510 --> 00:14:22,600
I’m a hostage.

226
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:24,510
Leaving the capital without permission is a felony.

227
00:14:24,780 --> 00:14:26,080
If I go back,

228
00:14:26,320 --> 00:14:27,160
Emperor will condemn

229
00:14:27,160 --> 00:14:28,270
the entire Yanbei.

230
00:14:29,560 --> 00:14:30,420
Then will father chain me up

231
00:14:30,420 --> 00:14:31,510
and send me back to Chang’an

232
00:14:33,380 --> 00:14:34,770
or wage a war against it?

233
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:35,800
Your Excellency,

234
00:14:36,700 --> 00:14:38,370
I’m afraid that the Emperor of Wei

235
00:14:38,370 --> 00:14:40,140
will accuse your father

236
00:14:40,370 --> 00:14:41,950
of treason

237
00:14:42,350 --> 00:14:43,720
even if you don’t leave.

238
00:14:44,320 --> 00:14:45,950
Things have come to that stage?

239
00:14:48,090 --> 00:14:49,370
So far, everything is fine.

240
00:14:49,970 --> 00:14:51,340
As long as Marquis still controls the army,

241
00:14:51,340 --> 00:14:52,740
his safety is guaranteed.

242
00:14:53,040 --> 00:14:54,860
But if you are held by His Majesty,

243
00:14:55,450 --> 00:14:57,140
however influential Marquis is,

244
00:14:57,380 --> 00:14:59,580
his life will still be in others’ hands.

245
00:15:00,200 --> 00:15:01,640
Only if you’re back to Yanbei

246
00:15:01,780 --> 00:15:03,400
will Marquis be spared from any concerns,

247
00:15:03,560 --> 00:15:05,520
then he can attack or defend as he wishes.

248
00:15:05,910 --> 00:15:06,780
Besides,

249
00:15:07,400 --> 00:15:08,900
if His Majesty has nothing

250
00:15:08,900 --> 00:15:09,550
on Marquis,

251
00:15:10,040 --> 00:15:12,290
he will start to be discreet.

252
00:15:13,040 --> 00:15:15,260
Your Excellency, time is running out.

253
00:15:15,260 --> 00:15:17,310
Please make the decision as soon as possible.

254
00:15:18,330 --> 00:15:19,660
I’m going back with you,

255
00:15:20,710 --> 00:15:22,690
plus someone else.

256
00:15:23,640 --> 00:15:24,580
Who is it?

257
00:15:24,860 --> 00:15:25,980
A girl.

258
00:15:25,980 --> 00:15:27,460
I have promised her that.

259
00:15:27,460 --> 00:15:28,740
Give me a few more days.

260
00:15:28,740 --> 00:15:30,080
She will leave with me.

261
00:15:30,080 --> 00:15:30,870
Your Excellency,

262
00:15:31,800 --> 00:15:34,460
