265
00:15:40,490 --> 00:15:42,020
If anything leaks,

266
00:15:42,020 --> 00:15:44,080
there will be

267
00:15:44,080 --> 00:15:45,400
dire consequences.

268
00:15:47,860 --> 00:15:48,840
Don’t worry.

269
00:15:49,050 --> 00:15:50,710
She is just an ordinary girl,

270
00:15:50,710 --> 00:15:52,110
and won’t leak anything.

271
00:15:52,700 --> 00:15:53,530
Besides,

272
00:15:53,880 --> 00:15:55,080
everyone knows

273
00:15:55,080 --> 00:15:56,370
that I will go back to Yanbei

274
00:15:56,370 --> 00:15:57,700
after celebrating Princess Chun’s coming-of-age.

275
00:15:58,320 --> 00:15:58,960
Now, we’re simply

276
00:15:58,960 --> 00:16:00,220
moving that up a little bit.

277
00:16:02,440 --> 00:16:03,630
If so,

278
00:16:04,130 --> 00:16:05,730
I will arrange everything soon.

279
00:16:06,920 --> 00:16:08,600
Please let your father know

280
00:16:08,820 --> 00:16:09,890
so that he can feel at ease.

281
