= Dear father =

282
00:16:23,570 --> 00:16:24,660
This is urgent.

283
00:16:24,980 --> 00:16:26,020
Deliver it as soon as possible.

284
00:16:26,020 --> 00:16:27,080
Yes, Your Excellency.

285
00:16:27,420 --> 00:16:28,880
I will send it out at once.

